<% layout("/layout/boilerplate") %>


    <div class="event-header">
        <h1>ASTECH in SIH Grand Finale 2024</h1>
        <div class="event-meta">
            <span><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i> December 11-15, 2024</span>
            <span><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 5 Days Event</span>
            <span><i class="fas fa-users"></i> In collaboration with ACES and Crieya</span>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/FFPgs2wk/astechgrp2.jpg" alt="SIH Grand Finale 2024">
    </div>

    <div class="event-detail-container">

        <div class="section-card">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>The Hackathon Final at our college was a thrilling five-day event that brought together tech enthusiasts
                from all walks of life to showcase their skills and creativity. As volunteers from the Astech Club, we
                had the opportunity to be part of this exciting event and contribute in several key areas. The event,
                which began on 11th December, required volunteers to work in shifts to ensure smooth operations and
                provide continuous support to the participants in collaboration with ACES and Crieya.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-sections">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-tasks"></i> Our Role</h3>
                <p>As ASTECH volunteers, we played crucial roles in:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Technical support and troubleshooting</li>
                    <li>Coordinating between participants and mentors</li>
                    <li>Managing event logistics and resources</li>
                    <li>Ensuring smooth communication flow</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section-card">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Impact & Learning</h3>
                <p>The SIH Grand Finale provided us with invaluable experience in:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Large-scale event management</li>
                    <li>Problem-solving under pressure</li>
                    <li>Team coordination and leadership</li>
                    <li>Exposure to innovative technologies</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section-card">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Participation Highlights</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Over 50 teams participated</li>
                    <li>24/7 support provided throughout the event</li>
                    <li>Multiple innovative solutions developed</li>
                    <li>Successful collaboration with industry mentors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

